{NORTH isn't sure just how much he can make, but surely 6\D isn't 
too much to hope for. 

He starts with a Gerber 4\C and SOUTH shows three Aces.

Hmmm, 5\C asks for Kings and SOUTH shows three.

Hmm, NORTH can now count all thirteen tricks, so he forgets about the \D 
slam and bids 7NT.}

